videos.description: Jordan Ford fakes out his Zags defender and pulls up for 3 from the top of the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ford hits Gonzaga's big man caught in a step-back 3) 2020/3/10

videos.headline: Ford hits Gonzaga's big man caught in a step-back 3

videos.description: Jordan Ford slices through Gonzaga's defense and hits a nice circus shot for Saint Mary's.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ford carves up Zags' D for nifty layup) 2020/3/10

videos.headline: Ford carves up Zags' D for nifty layup

videos.description: Joel Ayayi picks up the rebound and races down court, sliding past his defender with a nice change up and hits a layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Ayayi takes it coast-to-coast

videos.description: Drew Timme bullies his Gonzaga defender and spins to hit a bucket late in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Timme works Saint Mary's defense in the post) 2020/3/10

videos.headline: Timme works Saint Mary's defense in the post

videos.description: Killian Tillie cuts around the back of the pack and rises up to the hoop for a layup from Filip Petrusev.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Saint Mary's leaves Tillie open for smooth layup) 2020/3/10

videos.headline: Saint Mary's leaves Tillie open for smooth layup

videos.description: Gonzaga head coach Mark Few talks about Gonzaga's WCC victory, Drew Timme's outstanding game and looks head to the NCAA tournament.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Few 'pleasantly surprised' by Gonzaga's tenacity) 2020/3/10

videos.headline: Few 'pleasantly surprised' by Gonzaga's tenacity

videos.description: With a win over Saint Mary's, Gonzaga is officially headed to the NCAA tournament and celebrates with a round of confetti and placing their sticker on the board.
videos.headline: Gonzaga celebrates WCC victory
